original: Lalander, Kurt Mlllis, civilingenjör, Linköping, f. 24/1/10 i Östersund av ’landsfiskal A. J. L. o. Elsa Sandelin. G. 37 m. Ebba Malmgren. Barn: Susanne f. 40, Margareta 43. — Stud:-ex. v. Östersunds h. a. 1. 31, civ:ing:-ex. v. KTH 37. Anst. v. Sparmanns flygplanverkst. 36-37, h. Sv. Aeroplan A-B i Trollhättan 37-41, avdxhef v. Sv. Aeroplan A-B i Linköp. fr. 41. Skr.: Flygplankontroll (NKI-sk. 46).
translated: Lalander, Kurt Millis, civil engineer, Linköping, born on January 24, 1910 in Östersund to 'landsfiskal' A. J. L. and Elsa Sandelin. Married in 1937 to Ebba Malmgren. Children: Susanne, born in 1940, and Margareta, born in 1943. Completed secondary school at Östersunds h. a. 1 in 1931, and obtained his civil engineering degree from KTH in 1937. Employed at Sparmanns flygplanverkst. from 1936 to 1937, and at h. Sv. Aeroplan A-B in Trollhättan from 1937 to 1941. Became the head of Sv. Aeroplan A-B in Linköping from 1941. Wrote: Flygplankontroll (NKI-sk. 46) - Flight Control (NKI Publication 1946).
